        <div id="artwork-image">
            <img src="images/172260_2921716.jpg" alt="Poster-Newspaper Izogiza International Political Review" title="Boris Efimovich Efimov
(Born Kiev, 1900; died Moscow, 2008)
Dem&#039;ian Bednyi
(Born Gubovka, 1883; died Moscow, 1945), Poster-Newspaper Izogiza International Political Review"  />          </div>

    <p class="tools">
